      "body" : "@Iacas What do you mean by &quot;convert back&quot;? A <code>vararg</code> expects individual elements, and <code>*array</code> is the Kotlin way to say &quot;treat this array as individual elements for that purpose&quot;. Within the <code>vararg</code>-function the <code>vararg</code> parameter will be an array anyway. To convert individual elements to an array you can use <code>arrayOf(...)</code>, but you don&#39;t need that in this case."
