  "title" : "Convert Kotlin Array to Java varargs",
  "body" : "<p>How can I convert my Kotlin <code>Array</code> to a varargs Java <code>String[]</code>?</p>\n\n<pre><code>val angularRoutings = \n    arrayOf&lt;String&gt;(\"/language\", \"/home\")\n\n// this doesn't work        \nweb.ignoring().antMatchers(angularRoutings)\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/9863742/how-to-pass-an-arraylist-to-a-varargs-method-parameter\">How to pass an ArrayList to a varargs method parameter?</a></p>\n"
